		<FONT SIZE = 2>
	  
	 	
		<DD><DD>Toronto Ontario -- Commencing in 1997, the Mackenzie Master Limited Partnership (the "Master LP") will begin making distributions on an annual basis.  Currently the Master LP distributes its income on a quarterly basis.  The final quarterly distribution will be declared for the period ended December 31, 1996 and will be paid at the end of January, 1997.  The next distribution will then be declared for the period ended December 31, 1997.<BR><BR><DD>For further information, contact:<BR><BR><DD>Ann Savege (416) 922-5322, Vice-President, Fund Administration, Mackenzie Financial Corporation<BR><BR><DD>Alex Bright (416) 922-5322, Assistant Vice-President, Fund Administration, Mackenzie Financial Corporation
 
		 
