<H1>Pen Hsiang (Paul) Li, Professor</H1><P>

University of Minnesota, Department of Horticultural Science, 286 Alderman Hall, 1970 Folwell Ave., St. Paul, MN  5108; Telephone:  512-624-1757; E-Mail:  lixxx008@maroon.tc.umn.edu; Fax:  612-624-4941.<P>

Ph.D., Oregon State University, 1963.  <P>

Dr. Li teaches courses in plant cold hardiness and post-harvest physiology.  His major field of study is plant cold hardiness of horticultural crops.  His research involves elucidating molecular biochemical and physiological mechanisms of cold acclimation process. Dr. Li has edited the reference books Potato Physiology and Low Temperature Stress Physiology of Crops and the Proceedings of Plant Cold Hardiness; he also has co-edited two volumes of Plant Cold Hardiness and Freezing Stress and a volume of Advances in Plant Cold Hardiness.  He has authored over 130 papers published in various scientific journals, including two award-winning articles for the Journal of the American Society of Horticultural Science.  During sabbatical and quarter leaves, Dr. Li conducted research at the International Potato Center in Peru
and researched and lectured in Japan, China, and the former USSR.  <P>

Dr. Li, who is an elected American Society for Horticultural Science fellow (1984), provides leadership in organizing and fostering communication and cooperation in plant stress physiology at the international level and serves as a journal editor and peer reviewer of manuscripts, books, and grant proposals.  Dr. Li is on the graduate
faculty in horticulture and plant biological sciences.<P>

<H2>Classes Taught</H2><P>

<UL>
<LI> <A HREF="hort8062.htm">Hort 8062</A>.  Discussions in Stress Physiology. 
<LI> 
<LI> <A HREF="hort8065.htm">Hort 8065</A>.  Seminar:  Discussions in Postharvest Physiology.<P>

</UL>
<H2>Selected References</H2><P>

Li, P.H. 1991. Mefluidide-induced cold hardiness in plants. Crit. Rev. Plant Sci. 9:497-517.<P>

Xin, Z.G. and P.H. Li. 1992. Abscisic acid-induced chilling tolerance in maize suspension cultured cells.  Plant Physiol. 99:707-711.<P>

Zhu, B.L., T.H.H. Chen, S.T. Lee and P.H. Li. 1993. Complementary DNA cloning and characterization of an  ABA-responsive gene associated with the induction of freezing tolerance of potato (Solanum commersonii).  Plant Mol. Biol.<P>

