Strefeler, M.S. and TC. Wehner. 1986. Estimates of heritabilities and genetic variances of three yield and five  quality traits in three fresh market cucumber populations.  J. Amer. Soc. Hort. Sci. 111:599-605.<P>

Mauro, M.C., M.S. Strefeler, N.F. Weeden and B.I. Reisch.  1992.  Genetic analysis of restriction fragment length polymorphisms in Vitis.  J. Heredity 83:18-21.<P>

Strefeler, M.S., N.F. Weeden and B.I. Reisch.  1992.  Inheritance of chloroplast DNA in 2 full-sib Vitis  populations.  Vitis 31:183-187.<P>

