Tong, C.B.S., J.M. Labavitch and S.F. Yang.  1986.  The induction of ethylene production from pear cell cultures by cell wall fragments.  Plant Physiol. 81:929-930.<P>

Tong, C.B. and K.C. Gross.  1989.  Ripening characteristics of a tomato mutant, dark green.  J. Amer. Soc. Hort. Sci. 114:635-638.<P>

Tong, C.B. and K.C. Gross.  1990.  Characterization and partial purification of an ethylene elicitor from tomato fruit cell walls. Physiol Plant. 80:500-506.<P>
 
