<H2>Hort 3031.  Fruit Science</H2><P>

Instructor:<P>

<A HREF="hoover.htm">Dr. Emily Hoover</A><P>

Principles of tree and small fruit production in temperate climates.  Site selection, cultural and management practice, physiological and environmental control of plant development, dwarfing, growth regulating compounds, pest and weed control.  Lecture and laboratory.  (No prereq).  3 credits. <P>

