<H2>Hort 5042  Turf Grass Science</H2><P>

Instructor<P>

<A HREF="white.htm">Dr. Donald  White</A><P>

For advanced students in turf with career objectives in professional turf management.  All phases of the turf industry considered.  Emphasis on the ecology, physiology, and theory of turf population dynamics and on specialized management situations such as golf course, commercial sod production, and fine turf athletic settings.  (5 credits; prereq 3001, 3072, PBio 3131, PlPa 5001)<P>

