<H2>Hort 8065.  Discussions in Post Harvest Physiology</H2><P>

Instructor<P>

<A HREF="li.htm">Dr. Paul  Li</A> and <A HREF="tong.htm">Dr. Cindy  Tong</A><P>

Physical requirements and physiological basis of storage techniques used in maintaining quality in horticultural products.  Topics include historical evolution of postharvest physiology, biochemical and physical changes occurring during storage and senescence of horticultural products. (1 credit; prereq #)<P>

