refugia in recovery from disturbances:  modern fragmented and disconnected river 
systems.  Environmental Management 14(5):  711-724.<p>
Yount, J.D. and G.J. Niemi.  1990.  Recovery of lotic communities and ecosystems from 
disturbance:  theory and application.  Environmental Management  14(5):  515-762.<p><hr>
<A href="restecol.htm">Return to Restoration and Reclamation Ecology Home Page</A>
</body>
</html>
</DOC>
