<DOCHDR>
http://www.dis.mil:80/mission.htm 207.132.241.10 19970111232723 text/html 2898
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Sunday, 12-Jan-97 02:22:46 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 03-Oct-96 16:35:28 GMT
