<body background="/images/texture.gif">

<IMG SRC="/images/firetrck.gif" ALT="[Fire Truck}"><center><h1>Customer Service Center</h1></center>

<img src="/images/bar.gif">
<BR>
Customer Service Center (CSC) provides DIS-wide automated data processing support on such projects as the Industrial Security System (ISS), Field Information Management
System (FIMS1 and FIMS2), Local Area Network (LAN) problems to include LAN administration, server problems 
and password problems, cc:MAIL (email package) problems, maintenance and administration.  
We are also responsible for installing applications and configuring personal computers (PCs) for the Personnel
Investigations Center.
<BR><BR>
CSC also  provides support to customers outside of DIS such as DoD contractors and other DoD agencies. 
 Support provided outside of DIS includes support of the Electronic Personnel Security Questionnaire
 (EPSQ) software to contractor customers and military departments.   Also through Resource Access Control
Facility (RACF) we process and provide user ID for various mainframe accesses/privelges to other DoD agencies. 
<BR>
<HR>
The Customer Service Chief is C. Dan Ferguson

