<HEAD>
<title>Defense Clearance and Investigations Index</title>
<meta name="Author" content="Matt Martelli">
<meta name="Project" content="DCII">
<meta name="Server" content="Internet">
<meta name="Date" content="10-3-96">
<link rel="previous" href="/projects/index.htm">
</HEAD>

<frameset rows = "80%,20%">
<NOFRAMES>


<BODY background="/images/texture.gif">
<img src="/images/earth.gif" align=left>
<H1><CENTER>Welcome to the Defense Clearance and Investigations
Index (DCII) Home Page</CENTER></H1>
<br>
<H3>What is the DCII?</H3>

<P>
The DCII is a database of information originated by the Department
of Defense (DoD) and other federal agencies designed to be a central
index of clearance and investigative information on persons, companies
or events that have been the subject of DoD and other federal
agencies investigations.  The DCII supplies information in the
form of &quot;tracings&quot; to authorized agencies.  In addition
to investigative and clearance information the system contains
access determinations, aliases and statistics on transactions
by requesting agencies.
<hr>
<A href="index.htm" target="body"><IMG SRC="/images/cell1.gif" ALT="[home]" WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></a>
<A href="updates.htm" target="projectbody"><IMG SRC="/images/cell2.gif" ALT="[updates]" WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></a>
<A href="specs.htm" target="body"><IMG SRC="/images/cell3.gif" ALT="[Specifications]" WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></a>
<A href="under.htm" target="projectbody"><IMG SRC="/images/cell4.gif" ALT="[Specifications]" WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></a>
<A href="under.htm" target="projectbody"><IMG SRC="/images/cell5.gif" ALT="[Frequently Asked Questions]" WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></a>
<A href="under.htm" target="projectbody"><IMG SRC="/images/cell6.gif" ALT="[Point of Contact]" WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></a>
<p>
<a href="../index.htm"><img src="/images/back.gif" alt="back arrow" align=bottom width=40 height=40></a>Go back to the Projects home page. </p>
