<h1><center>Coming Soon</center></h1>
<br>
<dt><h2>Coming soon to: DIS Overview</h2>
<dl>
<dd><h4><img src="/images/ball_blu.gif"> Location of Defense Investigative Services Field Offices<br></h4>
<dd><blockquote>Contact information for field offices in each locality.</blockquote>
<hr>
<dt><h2>Coming soon to: DIS Projects</h2>
<dl>
<dt><h4><img src="/images/ball_blu.gif"> CCMS - Case Control Management System<br></h4>
<dd><blockquote>The CCMS is the heart of the DIS
Modernization Initiative.  The CCMS provides a framework for managing the Personnel
Security Investigation Program within DIS.  The CCMS matches the agency's need to redesign its
functional processes to meet the new realities of automation within the Department of 
Defense.  The CCMS will go into production in April, 1997.</blockquote>
<p>
<br>
<dt><h4><img src="/images/ball_blu.gif">FIMS - Field Information Management System<br></h4>
<dd><blockquote>FIMS1 currently provides Case Control information to the Field
Office which assists the Office Managers in administering their resources
and aids in the processing of Reports of Investigation.  FIMS2
will provide the agent in the field the ability to more easily 
communicate his work to the Field Office.  FIMS2 will be replacing
FIMS1 in most Field Offices over the next 6 months.</blockquote>
<p>
<br>
<dt><h4><img src="/images/ball_blu.gif">ISS - Industrial Security Software<br></h4>
<dd><blockquote>ISS will provide tools for IS personnel to effectively and efficiently schedule their
IS actions.  DIS management and, ultimately, other DoD components and User Agencies can view the
security status/posture of a DoD facility security clearance/ program.</blockquote>
</dl>
</dl>
