<DOCHDR>
http://www.dis.mil:80/projects/epsq/epsqdown.htm 207.132.241.10 19970111234634 text/html 6444
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Sunday, 12-Jan-97 02:41:52 GMT
Last-modified: Sunday, 20-Oct-96 20:13:56 GMT
Content-length: 6256
