<body background="/images/texture.gif">
<center><h1>How to find us at APS</h1></center>
<hr>
<! <img src="/images/aps10a.gif" alt="New building"><br>
<img src="/images/aps2map.gif" alt="Map of new location"><br>
<br>
You can also see the <a href="aps2map.htm">Airport Square</a> area map in greyscale, but it is a 600K file.
<br>
<hr>
<h2>Directions from Baltimore:</h2>
<strong>--> using 95 South:</strong>
<blockquote>
<ul>
<li>Travel on 95 going south, outside the 695 loop.</li>
<li>Pick up 195 going east, toward Baltimore Washington Airport (BWI).</li>
<li>Follow this until you get to the exit for 295 going north.</li>
<li>When you get on 295 going back north, the first exit you will see will be for West Nursery Road.</li>
<li>Take the West Nursery Road exit.  This should be a right hand exit straight onto West Nursery Road.</li>
<li>Follow the rest of the directions for finding us from West Nursery Road.</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>--> using 295 South:</strong>
<blockquote>
<ul>
<li>Travel on 295 going south, outside the 695 loop.</li>
<li>The next exit after the 695 loop will be for West Nursery Road.</li>
<li>Take the West Nursery Road exit.</li>
<li>At the stop light at the end of the exit ramp take a left on West Nursery Road.</li>
<li>Follow the rest of the directions for finding us from West Nursery Road.</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<br>
<hr>
<h2>Directions from Washington DC:</h2>
<strong>--> using 95 North:</strong>
<blockquote>
<ul>
<li>Travel on 95 going north, outside the 495 loop.</li>
<li>Pick up 195 going east, toward Baltimore Washington Airport (BWI).</li>
<li>Follow this until you get to the exit for 295 going north.</li>
<li>When you get on 295 going back north, the first exit you will see will be for West Nursery Road.</li>
<li>Take the West Nursery Road exit.  This should be a right hand exit straight onto West Nursery Road.</li>
<li>Follow the rest of the directions for finding us from West Nursery Road.</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>--> using 295 North:</strong>
<blockquote>
<ul>
<li>Travel on 295 going north, outside the 495 loop.</li>
<li>Just past the 195 exit, the next exit you will see will be for West Nursery Road.</li>
<li>Take the West Nursery Road exit.  This should be a right hand exit straight onto West Nursery Road.</li>
<li>Follow the rest of the directions for finding us from West Nursery Road.</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<br>
<hr>
<h2>Directions once you are on West Nursery Road:</h2>
<blockquote>
<ul>
<li>As you travel down West Nursery Road you will pass the Northrop Grumman building on your right.</li>
<li>Just past the Northrop Grumman building you will get to a stop light for Winterson Road.  You will turn right at the light onto Winterson Road.</li>
<li>The first light on Winterson Road will be for Elkridge Landing Road.  You will turn left at the light onto Elkridge Landing Road.</li>
<li>As you travel down Elkridge Landing Road you will pass a Roy Rogers on your left.</li>
<li>After you pass the Roy Rogers, also on your left you will pass Airport Square building #8.  In front of building #8 is also a sign for a Basils Deli.</li>
<li>After building #8, the next building on your left will be building #10.  This building has a fence around it and a guard station at the entrance.</li>
<li>We are located in building #10.  When you pull up, stop at the guard station and ask for directions.</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<hr>
