<h1><center>Deputy Director for Resources</center><br>
<img src="/images/nopict.gif" align=absbottom border=5 width=100 height=100> Mr. Willard Isaacs</h1>
<hr>
<h2>Biography</h2>
<p>Not currently available.
<hr>
<h2>The Office of the Director for Resources</h2>
<p>Responsible for providing the resources required to support the agency missions. Specific responsibilities include financial management (planning, programming, budgeting, execution, and fund control); logistics and administration (real property management, vehicle management, supply, correspondence, and mail); human resources; and internal management controls. 
Serves as principal advisor to the Director in assigned areas of responsibility and represents the Director before the Office of the Secretary of Defense, other Federal agencies and Congress. 
