<center><H2>                JOHN W. FAULKNER</H2>
<H3>                       DIRECTOR FOR DISCO<br>
                      DEFENSE INVESTIGATIVE SERVICE</h3></center>

<h2>Biography</h2>

<P>John W. Faulkner is the Director of the Defense
Industrial Security Clearance Office (DISCO) in Columbus,
Ohio.  Prior to his assignment as the Director of DISCO
on June 28, 1992, he was the Assistant Deputy Director
for Clearances and International Programs at the
Headquarters of the Defense Investigative Service (DIS).
Before going to DIS Headquarters, he served as an
Industrial Security Representative and as the Chief of
the Detroit Industrial Security Field Office.  He has
a bachelors degree in political science from Michigan
State University and a juris doctorate from the Detroit
College of Law.  He is an inactive member of the State
Bar of Michigan. 
