<html>

<head>
<title>DISCO Mission Statement</title>
<meta name="Author" content="Matt Martelli">
<meta name="Project" content="home">
<meta name="Server" content="Internet">
<meta name="Date" content="10-15-96">
</head>

<body background="/images/texture.gif">
<br>
<center><H2>DEFENSE INDUSTRIAL SECURITY CLEARANCE OFFICE</H2>
<H3>                    MISSION STATEMENT</h3></center>

<p>Operating under the directional guidance of the Director 
for Industrial Security, Defense Investigative Service, 
DISCO is responsible for determining the eligibility of 
those U.S. contractors under the purview of the Department 
of Defense and their personnel for access to classified 
information or material, domestic or foreign.  The 
objective of the security determination process is to 
assure that the applicant can be trusted with access to 
classified information on a continuous basis.  DISCO also 
accomplishes an international programs mission assignment 
of processing U.S. contractor personnel for visits to 
NATO, foreign governments and other overseas activities.
<br>
<hr>

<p><a href="/indhome.htm"><img src="/images/back.gif" alt="back arrow" align=bottom border=0 width=40 height=40></a> Go back to the Industrial Security page.
<hr>
<address>Author: Matt Martelli<br>
Revised: 15 October 1996</address>
