<BODY BACKGROUND="/images/texture.gif">
<H2>WARNING:</H2>
<hr>
Department of the Navy Automated Information Systems and related equipment are
intended for the communication, transmission, processing and storage of U.S.
Goverment information.  These systems and equipment are subject to monitoring
to ensure proper functioning, to protect against improper or unauthorized use
or access, and to verify the presence or performance of applicable security
features or procedures,  and for other like purposes.  Such monitoring may
result in the aquisition,  recording,  and analysis of all data being
communicated,  transmitted,  processed or stored in this system by a user.
<P>
If monitoring reveals evidence of possible criminal activity, such evidence
may be provided to law enforcement personnel.  Use of this system constitutes
consent to such monitoring.
