<body background="/images/texture.gif">
<H2><center>What's new!</center></H2>
<hr>
<P>
<h2><b>EPSQ 1.2c is released!!!!</b></h2>
<p>We have released EPSQ 1.2c, which contains patches only for your EPSQ 1.2a and EPSQ 1.2b software. We call this 
diskette the 1.2c Patch because it is being applied to repair and upgrade the software you are already using. Since the release 
of EPSQ 1.2a on September 1, 1995, we have been busy identifying and resolving problems reported by EPSQ customers. 
We also have implemented several changes requested by the Office of the Secretary of Defense (OSD).</p>
<p>In order to install EPSQ initially, you must download the EPSQ 1.2b software as well as the EPSQ 1.2c patch.</p>
<p>Customers who already have EPSQ 1.2a or EPSQ 1.2b software only need to download the EPSQ 1.2c patch.</p>
<hr>

<br>
