<head>
<title>DCII Updates Page</title>
<meta name="Author" content="Matt Martelli">
<meta name="Project" content="DCII">
<meta name="Server" content="Internet">
<meta name="Date" content="10-3-96">
<link rel="previous" href="/projects/dcii/index.htm">
</head>

<body background="/images/texture.gif">
<H2><center>What's new!</center></H2>
<hr>
<P>
The DCII has recently been converted from a Supra relational database
on a mainframe platform to an Oracle relational database on a
UNIX platform! The conversion has given the DCII a Windows look
and feel with point and click capability, iconization, etc.  This
&quot;new&quot; DCII has an online tutorial that a user can install
and uninstall separately from the application.  The tutorial has
interactive exercises to give the user a true idea of how to use
the DCII.
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<p><a href="index.htm" target="body"><img src="/images/back.gif" alt="back arrow" align=bottom width=40 height=40></a> Go back to the DCII home page. 
