<HEAD>

<TITLE>DCII Specifications Page</TITLE>

<META name="Project" content="DCII">
<META name="Server" content="Internet">
<META name="Date" content="10-3-96">
<LINK rel="previous" href="/projects/dcii/index.htm">
<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="Matt Martelli">
</HEAD>

<BODY background ="/images/texture.gif">

<H3>Hardware and Software Requirements for the DCII</H3>

<P>
The minumum hardware requirements are as follows:
<UL>
<LI>an Intel compatible 486 PC at 66 Mhz
</UL>

<UL>
<LI>512K conventional memory
<LI>16 MB of RAM
<LI>50 MB of free hard disk space
<LI>Pointing device (mouse or trackball)
<LI>28.8 v.34 modem or Network Adapter and connection to DISN
<LI>SVGA color monitor and video card for 800 x  600 graphics
<LI>2.1 compliant PCMCIA slot or reader (for future Fortezza compliance)
</UL>

<P>
The software requirements are as follows:
<UL>
<LI>MS-Windows 3.1 or Workgroups
</UL>

<UL>
<LI>TCP/IP software compatible with Oracle SQL*Net 2.2 supporting
PPP (i.e.
</UL>

<P>
SuperTCP Pro, Chamelion TCP/IP)
<UL>
<LI>MS-Word 6.0 (needed to print User Manual)
</UL>

<P>
