<h1>DCII Pages Under Construction</h1>
<img src="/images/underdig.gif" width="100%">
</center>
<p>We are always striving to expand this World Wide Web service. To get out as much information as we can to you, our customers, and to present it in a way that making finding what you want as easy as possible.
<p>To accomplish this we continue to build and refine our World Wide Web pages.
<p>With our goal to provide the best service possible, this section of the DIS World Wide Web service isn't yet available. As soon as it meets our rigorous configuration and control management and evaluation standards it will be included in our World Wide Web service.
<p>Thank you for your understanding.
