<FONT SIZE=2>Containers (See &quot;Storage and Storage Equipment&quot;)
<BR>
</FONT>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=2>Contractor Operations Abroad (Overseas Assignment)</FONT>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=2>     Access by Contractor Employees Assigned </FONT>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=2>          Outside the United States----------------------10-601</FONT>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=2>     General---------------------------------------------10-600</FONT>
<P>
