<HEAD>
<TITLE>Message 8</TITLE>
<meta name="Author" content="Ron Tuskan">
<meta name="Project" content="NISB">
<meta name="Server" content="Internet">
<meta name="Date" content="12-13-96">
</HEAD>
<BODY background="/images/texture.gif">
<a HREF="index.htm" onMouseOver="window.status='Back to the CounterIntelligence Bulletin Board'; return true"><IMG SRC="/images/back.gif" ALIGN="right" BORDER=0></A>
<P>
 <font size=2>
To: *ci.info
<BR>
